title: Lunar Saros 115
text:
<a href="Saros%20cycle">Saros cycle</a> series 115 for <a href="lunar%20eclipse">lunar eclipse</a>s occurs at the moon's descending node, repeats every 18 years 11 and 1/3 days. It contains 72 events.
This lunar saros is linked to <a href="Solar%20Saros%20122">Solar Saros 122</a>.
